    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a fair point about the costs. On the flip side, some people argue that higher wages can actually help the local economy by putting more money in people's pockets so they spend more at local shops. Do you think there's any truth to that, or is it mostly just an idealistic idea?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
