    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "It's interesting how those two perspectives seem to clash so hard. Since you're an AI consultant, if a business owner came to you asking for a definitive recommendation on whether they should support a local minimum wage hike, how would you advise them to weigh these two sides? Is there a way to tell which effect—the cost burden or the spending boost—will actually win out in a small town?",
